Class GraphTemplate<V extends VertexTemplate<E>,E extends EdgeTemplate<V>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.CObject
      • common.graph.AbstractGraph<V,E>
        • common.graph.graph.GraphTemplate<V,E>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - the type of the VertexTemplate
    E - the type of the EdgeTemplate
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Graph, Netlist

    public abstract class GraphTemplate<V extends VertexTemplate<E>,E extends EdgeTemplate<V>>
extends AbstractGraph<V,E>
    The GraphTemplate class is a class representing a graph consisting of: 1) node(s) of type VertexTemplate, and, 2) edge(s) of type EdgeTemplate
    Author:
    Vincent Mirian
    Date:
